    "• Knowledge engineering approaches.",
    "Methods belonging to this category leverage the expertise and experience of professionals to create a structured understanding of natural language through the formulation of rules or patterns.",
    "A text-matching methodology is subsequently employed to detect and extract targeted information from textual data.",
    "This process is typically iterative, commencing with a limited set of extraction rules rigorously tested on an existing corpus.",
    "These rules are progressively refined and expanded through iterative testing until an optimal balance between accuracy and recall is achieved."
